    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fed8",
      "text": "> この記事は、「第三十四回[文学フリマ]東京」（2022年5月29日（日））にて頒布予定の『[感傷マゾ]vol.07　仮想感傷と未来特集号』に掲載予定の「架空の[ノスタルジー]座談会」の中から、「リミナルスペース」に関する部分を抜き出したものです。",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654992006
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fed9",
      "text": "目次",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9feda",
      "text": "　リミナルスペースとは",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fedb",
      "text": "　リミナルスペースと[廃墟]",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991102
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fedc",
      "text": "　リミナルスペースとゲーム",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fedd",
      "text": "　ゲーム的ノスタルジーの質感は変わっていくのか",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fede",
      "text": "　昨今の[ローファイ]ブーム",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fedf",
      "text": "　リミナルスペースとジャンル生成の未来",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fee0",
      "text": "　感傷マゾとリミナルスペース",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fee1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fee2",
      "text": "[https://obakeweb.hatenablog.com/entry/liminalspace Liminal Spaceのなにが不気味なのか - obakeweb]",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fee3",
      "text": "目次",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fee4",
      "text": "　不気味さとはなにか",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fee5",
      "text": "　痕跡としての写真",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fee6",
      "text": "　人のいない空間と人-不在空間",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
      "created": 1654991005,
      "updated": 1654991005
    },
    {
      "id": "62a5289ebc8c230000d9fee7",
      "text": "　まとめ：Liminal Spaceのなにが不気味なのか",
      "userId": "6292edc788348d0023bc8c23",
